In terms of product type segmentation, the differentiation between pre-soaked and dry sheet masks allows companies to cater to diverse consumer preferences and needs. Pre-soaked masks offer convenience and ease of use, appealing to consumers seeking ready-to-use solutions. On the other hand, dry sheet masks provide flexibility for customization, allowing users to pair them with personalized serums or essences for a tailored skincare experience. This segmentation strategy enables market players to target different consumer segments and address varying demands within the Bio Cellulose Face Sheet market effectively.

